《'''波西傑克森—神火之賊'''》（{{lang-en|'''''The Lightning Thief'''''}}）是奇幻小說《[[波西傑克森|波西傑克森]]》系列當中的第一集，內容綜合了現代社會與古希臘文化，描述主角混血人波西傑克森被誤認為是偷閃電火的人，羊男保護他到混血營，並且與兩名同伴展開一場冒險。

== 概要 ==
《神火之賊》不斷採用古代[[希臘神話|希臘神話]]元素<ref name="thunder">{{cite web |url=http://thethunderchild.com/Reviews/Books/Childrens/Thomason/June/LightningThief.html |title=The Lightning Thief |last=Thompson |first=Kathy |work=The Thunder Child |accessdate=2009-09-01 |archive-date=2019-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191026034602/http://thethunderchild.com/Reviews/Books/Childrens/Thomason/June/LightningThief.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>結合現代場景。<ref name="Reviews List">{{cite web |url=http://www.rickriordan.com/Lightning_Thief_Reviews.htm |title=Reviews for The Lghtning Thief |publisher=RickRiordan.com |pages=1 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2008-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080420182407/http://www.rickriordan.com/Lightning_Thief_Reviews.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>內容偏向快步調、節奏<ref name="kreads">{{cite web |url=http://www.kidsreads.com/reviews/0786838655.asp |title=The Lightning Thief |last=Oksner |first=Robert |publisher=Kidsreads |accessdate=2009-09-01 |archive-date=2012-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120223143732/http://www.kidsreads.com/reviews/0786838655.asp |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="thunder" />及幽默風格。<ref name="Reviews List" />

=== 情節 ===
